THE E-KINGS.  The second mural, entitled The E-Kings, affixed in the Navigli area, aims to induce a reflection on the concept of "gift", something special since the dawn of time, which, in the times of E-commerce, has now become meaningless.
This is how the Magi, protagonists of the new work, no longer carry incense, gold and myrrh, but gift boxes purchased on large e-commerce platforms.

üáÆüáπ‚ÄùEuropean Parliament School Report‚Äù purtroppo √® durato meno di 12 ore. 
L‚Äôopera voleva essere un invito alla riflessione sulle sorti dei tanti bambini migranti che arrivano in Europa con mezzi precari, in condizioni disumane, e che una volta toccata terra, provano sulla propria pelle la scollatura tra le promesse di cooperazione internazionale da un lato, e la riluttanza all‚Äôaccoglienza dall‚Äôaltro. 
E voi che voto dareste al Parlamento Europeo? -
üá¨üáß "European Parliament School Report" sadly lasted less than 12 hours, until its removal was ordered by the City Council of The city of Florence . It  shows a black child, traveling on a paper boat, showing a report card, in which he gives his votes to the European Parliament on the degree of hospitality, humanity, solidarity, but also hypocrisy. An invitation to reflect on the fate of the many migrant children who arrive in Europe by precarious means, in inhuman conditions, and who, once they have landed, experience the cleavage between the promises of international cooperation on the one hand and the reluctance to welcome on the other. What note would you give to the European Parliament? -
